Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.43,0:00:17.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.43,0:00:17.77,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(478,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.93,0:00:27.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此所談到的未來  就是有你陪伴的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.11,0:00:31.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(519,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意成為你的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.57,0:00:43.05,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅信彼此牽在一起的雙手  發誓就這樣走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.16,0:00:49.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂我討厭你＂這句話  即使是玩笑話我也不忍說出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.92,0:00:56.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂我喜歡你＂這句話 如果不是事實我也不會說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.68,0:01:05.15,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你在無法見面時 沒有心思顧及其他東西一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這顆心  你想獨占
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.48,0:01:14.87,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fscy80\fscx120}{\pos(478,455)}{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.03,0:01:24.42,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我倆的愛分隔兩地  請你擁抱住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.29,0:01:31.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如膠似漆  心緒不寧的夜晚仍會造訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.59,0:01:39.35,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那時候 你要緊緊的抱住我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.10,0:22:40.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個星空如此閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.69,0:22:49.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些無論怎樣都是因為有了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.37,0:23:00.34,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有了你 我一個人是做不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.88,0:23:10.85,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映在眼睛裡的東西 全都開始歪傾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.01,0:23:21.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望遼闊的天空 星星多麼閃耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.90,0:23:32.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手觸不及星星 為何天空如此遙遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.49,0:23:37.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要與你相逢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.30,0:00:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近最喜歡與最討厭的距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.40,0:00:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兩人的推理與悬案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天、海洋以及南方群島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.17,0:00:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海灘上刻下關鍵的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.81,0:00:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.77,0:00:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.40,0:01:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是那個褐色短髮的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.31,0:01:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女生披頭散髮的 看起來沒什麼精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我猜穿的八成是老氣的連身泳衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.61,0:02:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是稍微有點蓬鬆而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.42,0:02:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜她穿的是黑色比基尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.93,0:02:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面的推理你真的不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.81,0:02:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和…和葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.31,0:02:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟小學生一起討論女生的泳裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.12,0:02:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父母要是知道了 會多高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.82,0:02:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是…是這小子說要看的 拗不過他嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.03,0:02:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次哥哥真是厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.20,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說今天和葉姐一定會穿豹紋的泳裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的猜中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.30,0:02:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹…豹紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件泳衣哪是豹紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.71,0:03:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Zebra 也就是斑馬紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.91,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹跟斑馬不都大同小異嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說在大阪說的紋路就是豹紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.12,0:03:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.72,0:03:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不會是在梅田的Bigman被我放了鴿子後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以還在鬧彆扭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 哪有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.43,0:03:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為一個不負責任的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區等了四個小時而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.47,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不生氣 完全不生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.10,0:03:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生…生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.51,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為要道歉才會帶妳來沖繩嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不是平次請我來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是跟著小蘭的爸爸來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位沉睡的小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是明天了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西名偵探的對決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 有自信嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.23,0:03:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自信 從來沒有過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.90,0:04:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有毛利小五郎絕不會輸給大阪毛頭的堅決信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好個神經大條的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤島的公主與龍宮城(事件篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人員集合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.23,0:04:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去檢查場地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢察場地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.20,0:04:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就是明天小五郎先生要去的小島啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.50,0:04:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個有無名屍和詭異文字的無人島嶼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.41,0:04:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關西的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先勘查場地雖說有點狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大叔在工藤的幫助下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一搶先解決案子 我多沒面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我們也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆先合手把謎題解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.11,0:05:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓在螢光幕前的人知道大阪與東京偵探的差別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.11,0:05:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是江戶(東京別稱)的偵探啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是發現無名屍的船浦島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱鬼龜島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼龜島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 島的前端跟海龜的頭一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.70,0:05:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼你跟叔叔會在這裡比賽推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.41,0:05:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只是去給小島打廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.01,0:05:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那座島的町長金城說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.22,0:05:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上常發生搶劫 綁架類的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有損小島的口碑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀光客日益減少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想趁此打廣告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變一些小島的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這座船浦島是町長的財產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得就算解開無名屍之謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會好到哪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到電視臺的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實剛才的竹富先生就是正式職員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.21,0:06:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的都是熟悉附近海域的在地人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.82,0:06:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從大阪來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼明天拍攝完的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.42,0:06:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起潛水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是本地人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好玩的在哪都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.53,0:06:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.90,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾天的行程都排滿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.20,0:06:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背著氧氣筒又弄上腳蹼跟隻企鵝一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們可沒有在海底陪魚兒散步的功夫 傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.32,0:07:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.12,0:07:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有關係 只是從小一起長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.22,0:07:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老愛煩人 老愛當跟屁蟲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.43,0:07:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對碰不得的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點誇大其詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才問說你是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上來船上的目的是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是工作人員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.70,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關西的名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.41,0:07:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服部平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.11,0:07:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次特別節目的主角之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他看起來像小孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才有意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.62,0:07:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嶄露頭角的高中生偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.52,0:07:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑戰毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我向那個少根筋的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話少說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊將工作完成早點收工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則就要天黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古索的使者會來討取瑪布依
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 船長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古索的使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討取瑪布依
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.52,0:08:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古索意指另個世界 瑪布依代表靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.53,0:08:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在沖繩流傳的古老傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說如果女人在半夜織布時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紡織針斷掉的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.20,0:08:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿黑衣的死神就會從海的彼岸緩緩靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她的魂魄吸走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少嚇唬人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.62,0:08:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想要到島上游泳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩的泳裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.81,0:09:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長 別激起那麼大的浪花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著黑色的潛水裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說這個島的周圍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.73,0:09:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導演在叫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了吧 該工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.41,0:09:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主沉睡之處是＂甲＂而非＂乙＂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.01,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的在這刻字的柱子前發現過屍體嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說當時屍體的背正靠著這個刻字上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.32,0:09:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因多日缺水斷糧而死亡的人 一年前發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據在地人說 正於一年前強颱持續多日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家猜想可能是因為遇颱而翻船的水手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.30,0:10:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流到這個島上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是誰也搞不清楚這些文字表達的涵義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.21,0:10:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 這幢房子是誰建的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人島上蓋了這種房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.32,0:10:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町長金城先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是作別墅的用意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.23,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來因為被強颱破壞就荒廢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 現在這裡與以前變化很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.11,0:10:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像浦島太郎的傳說一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.91,0:10:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您以前常來這個島嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前在船上看見這座島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島的四周可以捕到不少竹筴魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹筴魚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.42,0:11:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也常來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.33,0:11:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.13,0:11:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這座島的前端是很好的潛水區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從發現了無名屍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛水的同伴們都認為感覺不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就很少來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我和服部在這裡談事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先在島上隨便逛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看有無可疑之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找找有無破案線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.92,0:11:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 叫這群人尋找線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不信任我的專業嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.13,0:11:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主沉睡之處是＂甲＂而非＂乙＂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.20,0:11:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲和乙的意思大概是甲乙丙序之分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.90,0:11:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主寢於一而非二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 工藤 你有沒有什麼頭緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會明明知道什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.02,0:12:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你們東京贏故意裝蒜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.72,0:12:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是公主的睡相最美的意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是平常看起來很漂亮的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.20,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡相也不會難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是進退維谷的意思嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.51,0:12:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.01,0:12:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 平良小姐怎麼還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.22,0:12:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人在船上等一個多小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.72,0:12:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是還在潛水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.10,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從這邊的海岸找起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.41,0:13:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小姐 有聽到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.41,0:13:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.60,0:13:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平…平良小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.02,0:13:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是兩小時前被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被細繩勒住脖子而窒息死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手跟腿上都有細微的割傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.63,0:13:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是當時因為掙扎而被樹枝雜草劃到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.00,0:14:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之 兇手在森林把她殺害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意把她移到沙岸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不久前才逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還在沙灘寫下這麼不吉利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,＂我乃古索的使者＂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.12,0:14:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 偵探小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道他是不久前逃跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易判斷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方的沙灘留有漲潮的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.20,0:14:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說當時的海浪是打到那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.81,0:14:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在 海浪仍在字的下方一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意味著是退潮後寫上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則字就被沖走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.62,0:14:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是港口的後背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.62,0:14:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一小時前 都一直在船上等她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小鬼剛剛才出來找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.33,0:15:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞了整座島才找到她的屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說明了除了我們還有什麼人也在這座島上殺了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是件他殺案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.71,0:15:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我們還有別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.31,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和葉 妳有帶數位相機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.71,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 隨身攜帶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手錶型手電筒跟一隻拖鞋借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手錶是可以 為什麼要拖鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.33,0:15:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 充當參照物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.20,0:15:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不拍下來 晚會兒就被海浪沖走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.21,0:15:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼需要我的手錶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.91,0:15:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣 趁著還沒有漲潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快把小姐搬上岸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼平良小姐會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是海裡有什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.73,0:16:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海裡啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.00,0:16:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平良小姐一到島上就開始潛水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且特地在那個海域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是有什麼東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個海域…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.21,0:16:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先坐船回到對岸去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等明天天亮了再來調查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.82,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道這傢伙早料到我會阻止 才叫我脫掉一隻鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰快點攔住平次哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要去海裡潛水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啊 潛水有什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定海裡有什麼線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不清天高地厚的小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.81,0:16:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的海域很急 傍晚的時候潛水的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是專業潛水夫 也可能會溺斃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.22,0:17:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.72,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次 別潛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…有什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個黑色的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船錨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.92,0:17:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.83,0:17:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你遊的真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被沖過來的 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他早就知道水流很急嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.51,0:17:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大叔不是說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座島周圍可以捉到很多竹筴魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹筴魚是生活在激流裡的海魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.32,0:18:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專吃竹筴魚的海鷗也在這一帶盤旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.92,0:18:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你剛才這麼急著找平良小姐是為了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.92,0:18:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 她要是也在這片海域潛水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.30,0:18:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會被激流沖走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.80,0:18:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝酷也裝得太離譜了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在這麼危險的海域潛水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.61,0:18:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 我是為了要儘快解決案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.78,0:18:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平次哥哥不會為了想贏小五郎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.31,0:18:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才卑鄙的提前來搜索線索的吧 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…當然了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.52,0:18:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之 先把平良小姐的屍體運到船上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要運到哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說是船上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.60,0:19:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 船不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.91,0:19:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個船長不會見了死人害怕 所以先走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.21,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道有殺人事件的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.32,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有發現屍體的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 船長會不會是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們下船去找平良小姐的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說要先開船到島的後背
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.33,0:19:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了平良小姐 然後留下文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.40,0:19:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我和這小子正沿著海岸搜查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人盜船的話會被發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言歸正傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.21,0:19:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命案的關鍵都在那個船長身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救援到之前 先在小島上忍耐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.13,0:20:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上他們發現相關人員還沒回去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視臺的人會來找我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到島上檢查場地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.40,0:20:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是安排在昨天的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.61,0:20:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 因為昨天沒有處理好船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有告訴製作單位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告而來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.41,0:20:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道我們來了無人島嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.02,0:20:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我昨天跟他們說已經檢查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.32,0:20:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是想提高收視率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.03,0:20:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才跟那個船長串通好的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.30,0:20:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕…絕對不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.10,0:20:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭的爸爸遲早也會來找我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.81,0:20:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那裡等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這酒太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為你明天比賽加油的沖繩白酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.10,0:21:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你揭發案件的真相 毛利偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於結果是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.31,0:21:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有心理準備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.42,0:21:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 服部和你女兒他們怎麼還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是比賽前不想和我碰面而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.40,0:21:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是任性的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 別理那幫孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.00,0:21:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來喝個痛快 為明天加把勁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不醉不歸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.90,0:22:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的情況有點不妙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.02,0:23:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西真是有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.83,0:23:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個茶碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.50,0:23:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰當煙灰缸用過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我們來這之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.90,0:24:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有群人在這裡聚集過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.20,0:24:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什麼事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.11,0:24:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能不只一兩個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.21,0:24:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱＂古索的使者＂的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.11,0:24:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.51,0:24:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤島的公主與龍宮城(追求篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.42,0:24:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.62,0:24:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動駕駛器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.92,0:24:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集是謎中之謎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.23,0:24:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼不交給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.43,0:24:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個似乎比較困難
